<h3>Recaptcha Troubleshooting</h3>
<p>Some possible issues with Recaptcha.</p>
<ul>
	<li>the domain needs to read "localhost"</li>
	<li>the .env file needs to be changed to have your secret etc included.</li>
	<li>the page with the recaptcha div needs to have the correct data-sitekey!</li>
</ul>

 <code> &lt;div class="g-recaptcha" data-callback="enableBtn" data-sitekey="6Le2aCcUAAAAAO8g693E9uMACIv7L-DeAbDZc67-"&gt;&lt;/div&gt; </code>
  
